[SN]TITLE[SN]
Matty Pearson: Accrington Stanley defender signs new deal

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Accrington Stanley defender Matty Pearson has signed a new contract, keeping him with the League Two club until the summer of 2018.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The 22-year-old joined on a one-year deal from FC Halifax Town at the end of last season.
Pearson has made 25 appearances for Stanley, scoring twice.
"It's great to have my future sorted," he said. "This is such a warm club. You're welcomed wherever you go and whoever you speak to."
